Mngomezulu said  It is alleged that the
suspect who is between 25 to 30 years of age started to terrorise this areas
since 2014."The police are working around the clock and plead
with people to come forward with positive information to stop the suspect from
committing more rapes. "The suspect pretends to be a plumber from
municipality. Residents will then allow him to enter to their premises to fix either
leaking pipes or geysers."The manner he conducts himself it shows that he is
used to the area and the environment."In most cases he wears a black or brown beanie.  He speaks zulu, is very clean shaved, slender
but masculine and short in height.He operates anytime including weekends. Some of his
victims are school children. He targets them on the way from schools and takes
them to the veld where he rapes them. He is not a violent person but he does threaten his
victims. He is not using any transport he is always on foot.Anyone with information may contact the investigation
officer Warrant Officer Malebye on Cell no: 066 009 7366 or 079 471 8385 or
call the crime line 08600 10111.
